short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hide your freelancer.com earnings, make it confidential.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Often times we are not comfortable with third parties seeing our revenue or money, and as a freelancer, Hide My Money - Freelancer.com is solving it by allowing you to hide or show your freelancer earnings.

You don't need to keep doing this all the time as the extension will always remember your choice.

If you found this extension helpful, please support us at: https://www.patreon.com/software202 it means a lot to us!

Thank you.
